OL,2,MA 3 million dollar question: how fast
OL,4,Mdoes a muon wobble?
OL,6,CGavin Hesketh
OL,7,CSat 12:00-12:30
OL,8,CStage C
OL,10,GThe Muon g-2 experiment recently made
OL,11,Gthe most precise measurement ever
OL,12,Gcarried out with a particle
OL,13,Gaccelerator: how fast muons "wobble"
OL,14,Gwhen put near a magnet. This
OL,15,Gmeasurement is so precise, it opened
OL,16,Gup gaps in our understanding of the
OL,17,Guniverse, and was awarded the $3M
OL,18,GBreakthrough Prize in Fundamental
OL,19,GPhysics in 2026. As one of the
OL,20,Gresearchers involved, I'll explain
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
